General.Name: Softronic AB
General.Description: Softronic AB (publ) provides IT and management services primarily in Sweden. It offers AI, AML, automation, business development, case management system, cloud, customer relationship management, ERP systems, management, Microsoft, operation, security, analyses, UX/design, web, and system solutions, as well as e-commerce. The company was incorporated in 1984 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
